=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. Filing of documents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;D. Compliance of requirements of the Act&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;One Person Company’ means a company which has only one person as a member.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Specific provisions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. ‘One Person Company’ shall be mentioned in brackets below the name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. OPC shall have 1 member only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. minimum of 1 director&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. FORMATION OF OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. OPC shall state: the name of any other person who shall become the member of the OPC in case of death or incapacity of member.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Nominee shall give written consent&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. withdrawal of consent by the nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. nominee shall give a notice in writing to the member and the OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. member shall nominate a new nominee within 15 days of receipt of the notice of withdrawal of consent by the nominee and within 30 days file with the Registrar the notice of withdrawal and written consent of the new nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. Right of the member to change the nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. member is entitled to change the nominee at any time for any reason&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Same as (3.II.B.2)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;D. death or incapacity of member&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. member shall cease to be the member and nominee shall become the new member&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Same as (3.II.A)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;III. Eligibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. for member and nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(i) he is a natural person&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(ii) he is an Indian citizen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(iii) he is resident(at least 120 days in PFY) in India or otherwise&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. Prohibitions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. A minor cannot become a member or a nominee or hold beneficial interest in the shares of OPC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. a natural person shall not be -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(i)&amp;nbsp; a member of more than one OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(ii)&amp;nbsp; a nominee of more than one OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(iii) but can be a member in one and nominee in one other. In such a case if he becomes a member through nomination clause. Then he has to pick one OPC within 180 days&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;IV. Manner of passing resolutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36p