orandum, articles, etc to be given to members&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Any member of the company may demand from the company a copy of memorandum, articles and a copy of every agreement and every resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. company shall furnish to the member concerned, the documents demanded by him within 7 days of the request if the member pays the prescribed fees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;18. RECTIFICATION OF NAME OF COMPANY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. name is identical or similar to name of a company already registered&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. CG may direct the company to rectify its name.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. the company shall, within 3 months, rectify its name by passing an ordinary resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. name is identical or similar to name of a registered trade mark&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. proprietor of the registered trade mark may make an application to CG, within 3 years of -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(i)&amp;nbsp; registration of the company by such name; or&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(ii)&amp;nbsp; registration of the company by such a new name.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. On receipt of such an application, CG may direct the company to rectify its name.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. company shall, within 6 months, rectify its name by passing an ordinary resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;19. CONVERSION OF COMPANIES FROM ONE CLASS TO ANOTHER CLASS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Legal requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. company registered under the Companies Act by -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. alteration of its memorandum and articles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. complying with the provisions of Chapter II;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. making an application to the Registrar for the purpose of conversion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Registrar on satisfaction -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(a) close the former registration of the company;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(b)&amp;nbsp; register the documents filed with it; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(c)&amp;nbsp; issue a fresh certificate of incorporation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. Effects of fresh registration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The fresh registration shall not affect any debts, liabilities, obligations or contracts incurred or entered into by the company prior to such conversion, and may be enforced in the same manner as if fresh registration had not been done.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;20. HOLDING SHARES BY A COMPANY IN ITS HOLDING COMPANY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Prohibitions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(a)&amp;nbsp; A company shall not (either by itself or through its nominees) hold any shares in its holding company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(b)&amp;nbsp; A holding company shall not allot or transfer its shares to any of its subsidiary companies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. Exceptions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;a) Shares held as a legal representative&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;b) Shares held as a trustee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;c) Shares held before the company became a subsidiary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Out of the above 3 cases, the subsidiary shall have a right to vote at a meeting of the holding company only in case (a) and case (b).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;III. Effects of contravention&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Any allotment or transfer of its shares by a holding company to any of its subsidiary companies shall be void&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;21. SERVICE OF DOCUMENTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I.Service of documents on the company or any officer of the company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: none ; display: inline-block ; overflow: hidden ; width: 602px ; height: 688px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/NGxxVsHqKYV59TI4rGGJsf8fEuvsIfqHkBWDezO-OQ-IFbT7FGPbhf2TUsQ8qWN2FAffD_3GE1puALZIrlHlDhbJn-Ptu5MjRzwsx5CSDCxhvY3C7jdlJSDmWJD8_ukO3YfYKVDs=s0&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0px ; margin-top: 0px&quot; width=&quot;602&quot; height=&quot;748.2012515573476&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. Time consumed in delivery of documents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. notice of a meeting is sent by post - deemed to have been served at the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;expiration of 48 hours after the letter containing such notice is posted&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. any other document is sent by post - it shall be deemed to have been served at the time it is delivered in the ordinary course of post.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;22. Authentication of documents, proceedings, and contracts - requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Signing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. a document or proceeding requiring authentication by a company or contracts, may be signed by any KMP or an officer or employee of the company duly authorized by the Board&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. Common seal not required&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Authentication of a document is not required to be made under the common seal, if any, of the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;23. EXECUTION OF BILLS OF EXCHANGE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. Authorisation to execute deeds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;24. doctrine of &#39;ultra vires’&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Ultra means ‘beyond’ or ‘in excess of’ and vires means ‘powers’. Thus, ultra vires means an&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;act or transaction beyond or in excess of the powers of the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Effects of ultra vires transactions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. The transaction is void ab initio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. contract cannot become valid by estoppel or ratification.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. member may obtain an injunction order from the Court restraining the company from proceeding with the ultra vires contract&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. Directors responsible shall be personally liable to the company for breach of trust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. If the company acquires some property under an ultra vires transaction, the company has the right to hold that property and protect it against damage by other parties&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;25. DOCTRINE OF CONSTRUCTIVE NOTICE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;every person dealing with the company is presumed to have read the memorandum and articles. Further it is presumed that he has understood the provisions of memorandum and articles correctly, i.e. in the right sense&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;26. DOCTRINE OF INDOOR MANAGEMENT OR TURQUAND’S RULE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Doctrine of indoor management operates in favour of the outsiders. Outsiders dealing with the company are not required to enquire into the internal management of the company assuming that as far as internal proceedings of the company are concerned, everything has been done regularly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Exceptions to the doctrine of indoor management\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Knowledge of Irregularity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Negligence - Suspicious circumstances or unusual magnitude of transactions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. No knowledge of articles - if the outsider has not read the articles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. Illegal transactions - not available in case of illegal transactions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. Forgery - you cannot sue cos but the can sue people behind it&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
